    dc:description "Figure 3. Theosbaena loko sp. n. 2.4 mm. A 1, antenna 1; A 2, antenna 2; GN, gnathopod; P 1, Pereopod 2; UR, uropod; T, telson. All scale bars represent 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/460126" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/BDJ.8.e59528.figure4>
    dc:description "Figure 4. Theosbaena loko sp. n. 2.46 mm. LMD, left mandible; RMD, right mandible; MX 1, maxilla 1; MX 2, maxilla 2; MP, Maxilliped. All scale bars represent 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/460127" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/BDJ.8.e59528.figure5>
    dc:description "Figure 5. Theosbaena loko sp. n. 2.46 mm. P 3, pereopod 3; P 4, pereopod 4; P 5, pereopod 5; P 6, pereopod 6; P 7, pereopod 7. All scale bars represent 0.2 mm." ;
