    dc:description "Figure 1. Distribution of Theosbaena in the Oriental Region. (Left) T. cambodjiana in red circle, T. kiatwongchai in blue circle and T. loko sp. n. in green circle. (Right) Khao Chaison isolated karst system extracted from Google Earth." ;
